ir buka rute Pontianak -- Yogyakarta |url=https://m.antaranews.com/amp/berita/1078594/lion-air-buka-rute-pontianak-yogyakarta |website=ANTARA |accessdate=24 September 2019}}</ref>\n\n|[[NAM Air]] | [[Syamsudin Noor International Airport|Banjarmasin]],<ref>https://www.kompas.com/money/read/2019/04/26/112844326/nam-air-buka-2-rute-baru-di-kalimantan-mulai-1-mei-2019</ref> [[Soekarno Hatta International Airport|Jakarta\u2013Soekarno-Hatta]],<ref>https://www.flynamair.com/about</ref><ref>https://jambi.antaranews.com/berita/308789/seputar-nam-air-yang-patut-anda-ketahui</ref> [[Rahadi Osman Airport|Ketapang]],<ref name=\"Instagram\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BabSfbRDty5/</ref> [[Pangsuma Airport|Putussibau]],<ref name=\"Instagram\"/> [[Tebelian Airport|Sintang]],<ref name=\"Instagram\"/> [[Adisumarmo International Airport|Surakarta/Solo]]<ref>http://m.rri.co.id/surakarta/post/berita/788867/ekonomi/nam_air_pindah_rute_penerbangan_dari_solo_mana_saja_rutenya.html</ref><ref>https://m.solopos.com/nam-air-buka-rute-anyar-dari-bandara-adi-soemarmo-ke-luar-jawa-mana-saja-1046501</ref>\n\n|[[Sriwijaya Air]] | [[Soekarno\u2013Hatta International Airport|Jakarta\u2013Soekarno-Hatta]]<ref>https://www.airmagz.com/54069/jelang-imlek-2020-sriwijaya-air-tambah-rute-penerbangan.html</ref> \n\n|[[Wings Air]] | [[Rahadi Osman Airport|Ketapang]],<ref>https://agent.lionair.co.id/LionAirAgentsPortal/Default.aspx/</ref> [[Kuching International Airport|Kuching]] (temporarily suspended),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/metro/metro-news/2018/01/26/new-connection-to-pontianak-kuching-is-airlines-first-international-destination|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)]]|date=26 January 2018|accessdate=28 September 2019|title=New connection to Pontianak|last=Ling|first=Sharon}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/276862/wings-air-launches-pontianak-kuching-from-jan-2018/|title=Wings Air launches Pontianak \u2013 Kuching from Jan 2018|publisher=Routesonl