affic==\n===Traffic===\n{{Bar chart\n| title       = '''Overall Operational Statistics'''<ref name=\"dephub\">{{cite web|url=http://hubud.dephub.go.id/?id/llu/index/filter:category,0|title=Lalu Lintas Angkutan Udara Bandara Internasional Supadio|author=Indonesian Minsitry of Transportation|accessdate=12 December 2017}}</ref>\n| bar_width   = 19\n| width_units = em\n| label_type  =Year\n| label1  = 2002\n| label2  = 2003\n| label3  = 2004\n| label4  = 2005\n| label5  = 2006\n| label6  = 2007\n| label7  = 2008\n| label8  = 2009\n| label9  = 2010\n| label10  =2011\n| label11 = 2012\n| label12 = 2013\n| label13 = 2014\n| label14 = 2015\n| label15 = 2016\n| data_type = Passengers movements\n| data_max  = 3923988\n| data1  = 597,688\n| data2  = 835,546\n| data3  = 1,085,019\n| data4  = 1,124,225\n| data5  = 1,220,592\n| data6  = 1,378,529\n| data7  = 1,390,622\n| data8  = 1,581,931\n| data9  = 1,186,170\n| data10 = \n| data11 = 2,291,470\n| data12 = 2,307,322\n| data13 = 2,502,957\n| data14 = 2,713,259\n| data15 = 3,182,267\n| col2_data_type = Aircraft movements\n| col2_data_max  = 45755\n| col2_data1  = 16,113\n| col2_data2  = 19,196\n| col2_data3  = 21,186\n| col2_data4  = 20,151\n| col2_data5  = 17,591\n| col2_data6  = 17,898\n| col2_data7  = 17,461\n| col2_data8  = 9,440\n| col2_data9  = 11,135\n| col2_data10 = \n| col2_data11 = 21,198\n| col2_data12 = 22,779\n| col2_data13 = 23,626\n| col2_data14 = 25,184\n| col2_data15 = 28,732\n| col3_data_type = Freight movements\n| col3_data_max  = 100000\n| col3_data1  = 3,993\n| col3_data2  = 5,155\n| col3_data3  = 5,874\n| col3_data4  = 7,005 \n| col3_data5  = 7,726\n| col3_data6  = 9,017\n| col3_data7  = 9,227\n| col3_data8  = 12,400\n| col3_data9  = 6,904\n| col3_data10 = \n| col3_data11 = 26,518\n| col3_data12 = 7,729\n| col3_data13 = 17,305\n| col3_data14 = 15,368\n| col3_data15 = 16,399\n}}\n\n===Statistics===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:89%;\" cellpadding=4\n|+ The Frequency of Domestic Flights at 